'''巨嘴擬鴷'''（''Semnornis ramphastinus''）是[[新熱帶界|新熱帶界]]一種獨特的[[鳥類|鳥類]]。

==分類==
巨嘴擬鴷與其他[[巨嘴鳥|巨嘴鳥]]以往是分類在[[須鴷科|須鴷科]]中。但是根據[[DNA|DNA]]研究，[[新大陸|新大陸]]的巨嘴鳥與[[鵎鵼科|鵎鵼科]]較與[[舊大陸|舊大陸]]的巨嘴鳥接近。<ref>{{cite journal en|journal=The Auk|volume=111|issue=2|pages=389-397|last1=Lanyon|first1=Scott M.|last2=Hall|first2=John G|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v111n02/p0389-p0397.pdf|title=Reexamination of Barbet Monophyly Using Mitochondrial-DNA Sequence Data|date=April 1994|author=|access-date=2009-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010122524/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v111n02/p0389-p0397.pdf|archive-date=2008-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>故此，巨嘴鳥分支被認為是獨立的[[科|科]]，而巨嘴擬鴷與[[尖嘴擬鴷|尖嘴擬鴷]]一同被分類在Semnornithidae科中。

==行為==
巨嘴擬鴷是吃[[果實|果實]]的。牠們[[繁殖|繁殖]]會有很多幫手協助孵蛋及餵養雛鳥。<ref>{{cite journal en |first1=Carla |last1=Restrepo |first2=Marta Lucy |last2=Mondragón |date=1998 |title=Cooperative Breeding in the Frugivorous Toucan Barbet (''Semnornis ramphastinus'')" |journal=The Auk |volume=115 |issue=1 |pages=4-15 |url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v115n01/p0004-p0015.pdf |author= |access-date=2009-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100806060415/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v115n01/p0004-p0015.pdf |archive-date=2010-08-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

